            <div class="biography-framework">
                <div class="biography-section">
                    <h3>What is a Data Biography?</h3>
                    <p>A comprehensive record of your dataset's life story‚Äîfrom creation to your analysis</p>
                    <div class="archaeology-parallel">
                        <p><strong>Just like archaeologists document artifact provenance, we document data provenance</strong></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="biography-elements">
                    <h3>Essential Biography Elements:</h3>
                    <div class="biography-grid">
                        <div class="bio-element">
                            <h4>Origin Story</h4>
                            <p>Who created it? When? Why?</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bio-element">
                            <h4>Journey</h4>
                            <p>How was it collected, processed, shared?</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bio-element">
                            <h4>Transformations</h4>
