                </div>
                
                <div class="ethics-principle">
                    <h3>Attribution & Respect</h3>
                    <p>Always credit your data sources</p>
                    <p>Remember: these represent real people and communities</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="ethics-principle">
                    <h3>üß† AI Training Debates</h3>
                    <p>Many sites now restrict AI training use</p>
                    <p>Cultural researchers must be extra thoughtful about data rights</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="responsibility-box">
                <h4>Your Responsibility as a Digital Archaeologist:</h4>
